# CAN Serial
 
### Installation

```shell
$ antonio (linux) >pipx install python-can
installed package python-can 4.6.0, installed using Python 3.12.3
These apps are now globally available
    - can_bridge
    - can_logconvert
    - can_logger
    - can_player
